@baseUrl = https://localhost:7232

### Initialize Applications index
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/init


### Seed applications
# Bulk indexes applications from uploaded JSON file (streams without buffering)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/seed
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./applications.json

### Search - all applications (default: 100 results, newest first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Search - by product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "CashLoan",
  "size": 10
}

### Search - by channel and status
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "Online",
  "status": "Completed",
  "size": 10
}

### Search - by date range
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "createdAtFrom": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "createdAtTo": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "size": 10
}

### Search - by main applicant name (default when roles omitted)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Anna",
  "lastName": "nowak",
  "size": 10
}

### Search - by main applicant nationalId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nationalId": "52183539787",
  "size": 10
}

### Search - by spouse only (searches across main applicant's and co-applicants' spouses)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Anna",
  "roles": ["MainClient"],
  "size": 1
}

### Search - across main applicant and spouse
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Anna",
  "lastName": "Nowak",
  "roles": ["MainClient", "Spouse"],
  "size": 10
}

### Search - across all roles
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Piotr",
  "roles": ["MainClient", "Spouse", "CoApplicant"],
  "size": 10
}

### Search - combined filters
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "CashLoan",
  "channel": "Online",
  "status": "Completed",
  "firstName": "Piotr",
  "sort": "asc",
  "size": 20
}
